dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init languages.searchPanes.emptyPanes` paramater is `-type null`. 


        As standard, SearchPanes will hide the container that is meant to hold the panes if there are none to display. If a message has been declared then this will be shown in the place of the panes.





$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#example').DataTable( {
        dom: 'Sfrtip',
        language: {
            searchPanes: {
                 emptyPanes: 'There are no panes to display. :/'
            }
        }
    });
});
